PROBLEM: I/P-> S="SUDHANSHU"
         O/P-> "UHSNAHDUS"
         
SOLUTION:

Method1-
    string reverseWord(string str){

        int n = str.size();
        for(int i=0; i<n/2; i++){
            swap(str[i], str[n-i-1]);
        }
        return str;
    }
    
 Method 2-
     use simply 'reverse(str.begin(), str.end());
                 return str;'
